{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011ControlItemB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for control-item-layout-based component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the control-item-layout-based component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._500 }","","        override var colorBgFocus: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.contentDefault }","","        override var spaceRowGap: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineTall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: ControlItemComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","tex